description:
Don't be fooled by his ranger outfit and love for nature, Android 17 is one of the most powerful warriors of Universe 7, and he will prove it once again in DRAGON BALL FIGHTERZ.

This content includes:
• Android 17 as a new playable character
• 5 alternative colors for his outfit
• Android 17 Lobby Avatar
• Android 17 Z Stamp
name: DRAGON BALL FIGHTERZ - Android 17
